<TITLE> American shot dead in Peshawar: Pakistani police </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 PESHAWAR, Pakistan, Nov 12 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Gunmen shot dead a US aid official along with his driver in the northwestern Pakistani city of Peshawar Wednesday, a senior police official said. "He was working for US aid projects for tribal areas," the official, who requested anonymity, told Reuters. US embassy officials in Islamabad were not immediately available for comment
